data.description: This 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath home in Palo Verde Estates is a great find! It features two separate living areas, larger bedrooms than normal, a sunken living room, and a very spacious laundry room. It has new paint inside and has been very well maintained. Outside you'll find a huge covered patio, storage shed, and a 2 car carport. Located near MCAS and great access to YPG!
